'''韓國總理室非法監控民間人士事件'''（{{lang-ko|민간인 불법사찰 사건}}）是2010年一宗發生於[[韓國|韓國]]的監控事件。這次事件由{{Link-ko|韓國國務總理室|대한민국 국무총리실}}引發，當時總理室轄下的公正倫理支援官室（{{lang|ko|공직윤리지원관실}}）對一位{{Link-ja|民間人士|民間人}}作出了監控行為，而此事件於2012年[[2012年大韓民國國會選舉|韓國國會選舉]]再次獲得了社會關注<ref>{{cite news | first = Min-uck | last = Chung | title = Surveillance case reemerges as polls near | date = 2012-03-13 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2012/03/117_106855.html | work = Korea Times | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923055921/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2012/03/117_106855.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Sebastián_Piñera_-_Lee_Myung-bak_(cropped).jpg|200px]][[李明博|李明博]]]]
監控事件起源來自一段名為「{{lang|ko|쥐코}}」（意指老鼠，此字經常被[[朝鮮|朝鮮]]當局用作攻擊李明博）、長25分鐘的影片<ref name=herald>{{cite news | first = Sang-ho | last = Song | title = Prosecutors reopen probe of 2010 illegal surveillance case | date = 2012-03-16 | url = http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20120316000903 | work = Korea Herald | accessdate = 2012-03-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110508/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20120316000903 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=atimes>{{cite web|author1=James Pearson|title=Seoul takes aim at Internet critics|url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Korea/NG26Dg01.html|publisher=Asia Times|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2012-07-26|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702083132/http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Korea/NG26Dg01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該影片由一名居住於美國的韓籍學生於2008年製作，內容改編自電影《[[健保真要命|-{zh:健保真要命;zh-hans:医疗内幕;zh-hk:美國清一Sick檔案;zh-tw:健保真要命}-]]》，全片圍繞著對[[大韓民國總統|總統]][[李明博|李明博]]濫用職權和官商勾結的批評<ref>{{cite news | author = 박영출 | coauthors = 신보영 | title = 김종익씨 ‘쥐코’ 동영상이 사찰 발단 | date = 2010-07-05 | url = http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2010070501070323031004 | work = Munhwa Ilbo | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001713/http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2010070501070323031004 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。作為前總統[[盧武鉉|盧武鉉]]支持者<ref name=herald/>，銀行職員金鐘益（音譯，{{lang|ko|김종익}}）在同年把影片分享到網誌上，但他其後隨即被總理室監控調查，引發社會上一連串對[[韓國網絡審查|韓國網絡審查]]的爭議<ref>{{cite news | author = 한윤형 | title = 왜 ‘민간인 불법사찰 증거인멸’에 주목해야 할까? | date = 2012-03-05 | url = http://www.mediaus.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=23673 | work = MediaUs | accessdate = 2012-04-05 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031703/http://www.mediaus.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=23673 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

金鐘益在2010年公開指控國務總理室對他進行了監控，後來卻被標籤為親朝鮮[[左翼|左翼]]份子<ref name=atimes/>，最後被逼辭職並移居到[[日本|日本]]，同時欠下大筆債款。他表示網絡上有許多人都發佈了相同的影片，不明白為甚麼只有自己被針對<ref>{{cite news | author = 정락인 | title=인간관계까지 철저히 파괴돼…나는 대한민국의 국민이 아니었다 | date = 2012-03-21 | url = http://www.sisapress.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=57441 | work = Sisa Journal | accessdate = 2012-04-05}}</ref>。

== 調查過程和後續發展 ==
[[File:Korea-Seoul-Blue_House_(Cheongwadae)_Reception_Center_0688&9-07_cropped.jpg|200px]]]]
2010年7月7日，{{link-en|大韓民國檢察廳|Supreme Prosecutors' Office of the Republic of Korea}}搜查了[[大韓民國國務總理|國務總理室]]<ref>{{cite news | first = Ji-sook | last = Bae | title = Prosecution raids PM’s office | date = 2010-07-09 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2010/07/117_69141.html | work = Korea Times | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2010-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100712142857/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2010/07/117_69141.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，這是韓國歷史上首次強制搜查總理室轄下的部門<ref>{{cite web|title=韓總理室涉嫌非法監察平民被查|url=http://news.wenweipo.com/2010/07/10/IN1007100076.htm|publisher=[[文汇报_(上海)|文匯報]]|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2010-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923061140/http://news.wenweipo.com/2010/07/10/IN1007100076.htm|archive-date=2015-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。檢察廳發現有官員合謀掩藏部分重要文件<ref>{{cite news | first = Si-soo | last = Park | title = PM’s Office suspected of concealing key evidence | date = 2010-07-11 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2011/04/117_69193.html | work = Korea Times | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923060250/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2011/04/117_69193.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。總統府就業與勞工關係秘書李泳鎬（音譯，{{lang|ko|이영호}}）在調查期間被禁止出國，然而檢察廳最後只檢控了七名低階官員<ref name=kt117/>。

2012年3月，檢察廳決定在公正倫理支援官室官員張真壽（音譯，{{lang|ko|장진수}}）的證言下重新開始調查<ref name=herald/>。張真壽供稱曾在警方搜查辦公室前兩天被[[青瓦台|總統府]]命令銷毀監控金鐘益的證據，並在2011年被總統秘書李泳鎬（音譯，{{lang|ko|이영호}}）以二千萬[[韓圓|韓圓]]嘗試賄賂他，要求他將總統府在事件中的角色保密<ref name=herald/><ref name=kt117>{{cite news | first = Hyo-sik | last = Lee | title = Key figures in surveillance scandal face summons | date = 2012-03-18 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2012/03/117_107184.html | work = Korea Times | accessdate = 2012-03-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224114/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2012/03/117_107184.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。4月3日，李泳鎬和另一總統府官員崔鍾錫（音譯，{{lang|ko|최종석}}）因涉嫌命令張真壽銷毀事件相關證據而被逮捕<ref>{{cite news | title = Two Key Figures In Surveillance Scandal Arrested | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.arirang.co.kr/News/News_View.asp?nseq=127595&code=Ne2&category=2 | work = Arirang news | accessdate = 2012-03-04 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053124/http://www.arirang.co.kr/News/News_View.asp?nseq=127595&code=Ne2&category=2 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = He-suk | last = Choi | title = Surveillance scandal grows, key figures arrested | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20120404001088 | work = Korea Herald | accessdate = 2012-04-04 | archive-date = 2012-04-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406141113/http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20120404001088 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。4月4日，張真壽公開了一些相片，證明他從國務總理室官員劉忠烈（音譯，{{lang|ko|류충렬}}）取得了五千萬韓圓的賄款，作為銷毀證據的回報<ref>{{cite news | first = Hyeon-jun (현준) | last = Kim (김) | title=장진수씨에 전달된 '관봉 5천만원' 사진 공개 | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/society/2012/04/04/0701000000AKR20120404104700004.HTML | work = Yonhap News | accessdate = 2012-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = 최지용 | title = 청와대 '5천만원 돈다발' 찰칵! 충격입니다 '증거인멸' 무마용... 5만원권 1000장 '비닐 포장 | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.ohmynews.com/NWS_Web/view/at_pg.aspx?CNTN_CD=A0001717296&CMPT_CD=E0942 | work = OhMyNews | accessdate = 2012-04-04 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023032/http://www.ohmynews.com/NWS_Web/view/at_pg.aspx?CNTN_CD=A0001717296&CMPT_CD=E0942 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 社會反應 ==
由於第二次調查發生於[[2012年大韓民國總統選舉|2012年大韓民國總統選舉]]期間，政界開始爭論監聽行為是否只發生於盧武鉉執政時期、還是在李明博上任後依然延續<ref>{{cite news | title = "내연녀와 모텔에…" 盧정부때 사찰문서 입수 | date = 2012-04-05 | url = http://news.donga.com/Politics/3/00/20120406/45328894/1 | work = Donga Ilbo | accessdate = 2012-04-05 | archive-date = 2015-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402093249/http://news.donga.com/Politics/3/00/20120406/45328894/1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年3月8日，韓國最大反對黨[[民主黨_(大韓民國2011年)|民主黨]]要求政府重新徹查事件<ref>{{cite news | first = Sun-young | last = Lee | title = Opposition demands reopening probe on surveillance scandal | date = 2012-03-13 | url = http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20120313000973 | work = Korea Herald | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2012-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120313134038/http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20120313000973 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此前，正在[[罷工|罷工]]的[[韓國放送公社|韓國放送公社]]工會曾經宣稱從李明博政府手上取得了2,619份監聽報告<ref>{{cite news | title = More than 2,600 Cases of Illegal Surveillance by PM Office Surface | date = 2012-03-30 | url = http://www.arirang.co.kr/News/News_View.asp?nseq=127491&code=Ne2&category=2 | work = Arirang News | accessdate = 2012-03-30 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923060543/http://www.arirang.co.kr/News/News_View.asp?nseq=127491&code=Ne2&category=2 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Lee gov't draws flak for fresh revelations in surveillance scandal | date = 2012-03-30 | url = http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2012/03/30/25/0301000000AEN20120330002500315F.HTML | work = Yonhap News | accessdate = 2012-03-30 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923060837/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2012/03/30/25/0301000000AEN20120330002500315F.HTML | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並上傳了一部分檔案，顯示國務總理室在2008至2010年間展開了範圍甚廣的監控行動，監控對象除了有公務員外，也包括了公共企業高級人員、政治家、大企業總裁、傳媒界和金融界人士、以至普通民眾<ref>{{cite web|title=韩国总理室非法监察民间人士被曝光|url=http://www.xbsb.com.cn/xbsbnews/news/jnews/2012-04-02/224802.html|publisher=国际在线|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2012-04-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923085535/http://www.xbsb.com.cn/xbsbnews/news/jnews/2012-04-02/224802.html|archivedate=2015-09-23}}</ref><ref name=ny10>{{cite web|author1=CHOE SANG-HUN|title=In South Korea Scandal, Echoes of Watergate|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/10/world/asia/government-spying-charges-complicate-korean-vote.html?_r=0|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2012-04-09}}</ref>。兩名[[大韓民國國家情報院|大韓民國國家情報院]]前院長[[高泳耇|高泳耇]]和[[金萬福|金萬福]]均否認了相關指控<ref>{{cite news | author = 김상만 | title = 참여정부 국정원장들 "정치사찰 없었다" | date = 2012-04-04 | url = http://www.mediatoday.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=101496 | work = Media Today | accessdate = 2012-04-04 | archive-date = 2012-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120405174433/http://www.mediatoday.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=101496 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。放送公社工會在兩人否認後透過[[Twitter|Twitter]]批評兩人說謊，但瞬即刪除了該貼文並道歉<ref>{{cite news | title = 靑 "민간인 사찰 대부분 노무현 때…" | date = 2012-03-31 | url = http://news.donga.com/Politics/3/00/20120331/45191375/1 | work = Donga Ilbo | accessdate = 2012-03-31 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923061256/http://news.donga.com/Politics/3/00/20120331/45191375/1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。放送公社記者後來反駁了兩人的言論，稱包含重複對象在內的監控個案合共有2,837宗，當中2,356宗發生於盧武鉉執政時期，而其中10宗針對平民<ref>{{cite news | first = Jae-jin (재진) | last = Lee (이) | title = 참여정부 국정원장들 "정치사찰 없었다" | date = 2012-04-01 | url = http://www.mediatoday.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=101422 | work = Media Today | accessdate = 2012-04-05 | archive-date = 2012-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402222635/http://www.mediatoday.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=101422 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2015年7月14日，韓國國家情報院在國會會議上承認曾經在2012年1月和7月從[[意大利|意大利]]購買一款黑客軟件，該軟件可以用於盜取電腦數據、以及遠程操控[[智能手機|智能手機]]和電腦，但情報院聲稱軟件純屬用於研究，從未用於監聽韓國公民<ref>{{cite web|title=韓國諜報機構購買黑客軟件 否認監聽民眾|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-07/16/c_128023455.htm|publisher=[[新華社|新華社]]|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2015-07-16|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923064845/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-07/16/c_128023455.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[韓國時報|韓國時報]]》和《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》將事件稱為「韓國的[[水門事件|水門事件]]」<ref>{{cite news | title = Watergate of Korea | date = 2012-03-14 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/opinon/2012/03/202_106924.html | work = Korea Times | accessdate = 2012-03-19 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040124/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/opinon/2012/03/202_106924.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = In South Korea Scandal, Echoes of Watergate | date = 2012-04-09 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/10/world/asia/government-spying-charges-complicate-korean-vote.html | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2012-04-29 | archive-date = 2012-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120415183046/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/10/world/asia/government-spying-charges-complicate-korean-vote.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

